Furnas has requested us to include in the contract a language saying that in case of rationing in Brazil the contracted energy is reduced proportionally. We plan to cap that reduction in 10%. I would like to know what would be the impact in the MTM treatment. I guess it doesn't affect MTM because a rationing could be seen as a Force Majeure event.

Please let me know what you think.

